{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Updated on January 25, 2025 Latest version [2.0.4]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/extras/catchphrase_EN.png?t=1737802761\" />When the protagonist wakes up, they find themselves lost in a different world. As they learn the words of the mysterious monsters that speak a strange language, they search for a way to escape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/extras/\u6587\u5b57\u89e3\u8bfb-\u82f1.png?t=1737802761\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this alternate world, a different language is used. Players will interpret and dechiper characters' words through expressions, gestures and the objects they point to.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/extras/play1_EN.jpg?t=1737802761\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The language of this world isn\u2019t as refined as human languages. One meaning is concentrated in one word, with almost no particles; a string of words conveys only a rough meaning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/extras/\u6050\u6016\u8131\u51fa-\u82f1.png?t=1737802761\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a point-and-click adventure game. Players will investigate items to learn words or engage in conversation to progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/extras/play2.jpg?t=1737802761\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choices for actions are available at various points. Small changes in development, branching paths, or even instant death can occur.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/extras/play3.jpg?t=1737802761\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Even if you reach a game over, you can retry from just before without any penalties. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There\u2019s no affection management, and acquiring flags will unlock more choices. Players can freely jump back to previously encountered scenes from chapters and try again. Play comfortably and easily!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/extras/endlist.jpg?t=1737802761\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are 20 types of mid-story endings (bad endings or unresolved problems).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are a total of 17 endings, including character route endings and late-stage endings upon reaching Chapter 5.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">*Note: There is a fake ending presented as a happy ending midway through the story, so please be careful not to misunderstand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/extras/line.png?t=1737802761\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25c6Playtime</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It takes about 5 hours to complete one full playthrough of all routes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>*This game is designed with replayability in mind, where understanding character conversations may require re-watching scenes after filling up the dictionary.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25c6Playing without sound is not recommended (There are sound-based effects).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players who want to make the characters say funny things or try different playful approaches are also welcome to enjoy the game freely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u3000</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737802761","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/page.bg.jpg?t=1737802761","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/7c8afe40743e83bb1ade4288212bcd427d4422d9/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737802761","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/7c8afe40743e83bb1ade4288212bcd427d4422d9/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737802761","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Updated on January 25, 2025 Latest version [2.0.4]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/extras/catchphrase_EN.png?t=1737802761\" />When the protagonist wakes up, they find themselves lost in a different world. As they learn the words of the mysterious monsters that speak a strange language, they search for a way to escape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/extras/\u6587\u5b57\u89e3\u8bfb-\u82f1.png?t=1737802761\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this alternate world, a different language is used. Players will interpret and dechiper characters' words through expressions, gestures and the objects they point to.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/extras/play1_EN.jpg?t=1737802761\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The language of this world isn\u2019t as refined as human languages. One meaning is concentrated in one word, with almost no particles; a string of words conveys only a rough meaning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/extras/\u6050\u6016\u8131\u51fa-\u82f1.png?t=1737802761\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a point-and-click adventure game. Players will investigate items to learn words or engage in conversation to progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/extras/play2.jpg?t=1737802761\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choices for actions are available at various points. Small changes in development, branching paths, or even instant death can occur.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/extras/play3.jpg?t=1737802761\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Even if you reach a game over, you can retry from just before without any penalties. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There\u2019s no affection management, and acquiring flags will unlock more choices. Players can freely jump back to previously encountered scenes from chapters and try again. Play comfortably and easily!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/extras/endlist.jpg?t=1737802761\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are 20 types of mid-story endings (bad endings or unresolved problems).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are a total of 17 endings, including character route endings and late-stage endings upon reaching Chapter 5.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">*Note: There is a fake ending presented as a happy ending midway through the story, so please be careful not to misunderstand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/extras/line.png?t=1737802761\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25c6Playtime</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It takes about 5 hours to complete one full playthrough of all routes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>*This game is designed with replayability in mind, where understanding character conversations may require re-watching scenes after filling up the dictionary.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25c6Playing without sound is not recommended (There are sound-based effects).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players who want to make the characters say funny things or try different playful approaches are also welcome to enjoy the game freely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u3000</p>","developers":["\u516b\u540d\u6728Games","\u6591\u4f01\u753b"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302660/header.jpg?t=1737802761","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> macOS 10.12 Sierra\u4ee5\u964d<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core 2 Duo<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> Intel HD Graphics 3000</li></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256951769,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256951769/movie480.mp4?t=1726742784","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256951769/movie_max.mp4?t=1726742784"},"name":"PV","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com